Markowski (feminine: Markowska, plural: Markowscy) is a Polish surname. It may refer to:Andrzej Markowski, Polish composerKrzysztof Markowski, Polish footballerPaul Markowski, American meteorologist and tornado expertTomasz Markowski (disambiguation)Vincent Markowski, birth name of American actor known professionally as Tom TylerAlfreda Markowska, Polish Porajmos survivor